description.en: Kitsune Inu is going to create a revolutionary ecosystem to bring more people into digital assets, helping to earn a passive income through redistribution / reflection, by holding the $KITSU token long term. This comes along with maintaining their privacy, security, power, and autonomy. We will use the community to create an ecosystem based on sound monetary policies, with a sound and solid decentralized foundation, that should be expected with the $KITSU digital asset.
